OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,7,Flooks at Keir Starmer's legacy in the
OL,8,FNorth East
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer's relationship with
OL,11,Four region has been a rollercoaster
OL,12,Fride.
OL,14,FA year after he became Labour leader,
OL,15,Fhe lost the high-profile Hartlepool by-
OL,16,Felection in May 2021, and considered
OL,17,Fquitting.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
