OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe then pledged to stand down if he
OL,7,Fwas found have broken Covid lockdown
OL,8,Frules by having a beer and a curry at
OL,9,Fan MP's office in Durham.
OL,11,FThe police cleared him, and the
OL,12,Fscandal surrounding Boris Johnson's
OL,13,Fparties in Downing Street during the
OL,14,Fpandemic triggered the Conservatives'
OL,15,Fmeltdown.
OL,17,FNorth Yorkshire MP Rishi Sunak was
OL,18,FStarmer's opponent at the 2024 general
OL,19,Felection, when Labour won 26 of the 27
OL,20,Fseats in the North East on their way
OL,21,Fto a landslide.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
