OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FBut among the many decisions he's made
OL,7,Fas Prime Minister, few were as fateful
OL,8,Fas appointing former Hartlepool MP
OL,9,FPeter Mandelson as Britain's
OL,10,Fambassador to the United States -
OL,11,Fdespite Lord Mandelson's links to sex
OL,12,Foffender Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,14,FBrutal election results around the UK
OL,15,Flast month - including Labour losing
OL,16,Fcontrol of Gateshead, South Tyneside
OL,17,Fand Sunderland councils to Reform UK -
OL,18,Fpretty much sealed Starmer's fate.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
