OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FAfter announcing his resignation on
OL,7,FMonday (22 June), he'll just make it
OL,8,Fpast two years in the top job - so
OL,9,Fjudging his impact on the North East
OL,10,Fis tricky.
OL,12,FMost obvious - his government
OL,13,Fcancelled plans to upgrade 13 miles of
OL,14,Fthe A1 in Northumberland to dual
OL,15,Fcarriageway, saying the scheme was
OL,16,F"poor value for money".
OL,18,FBut, they did announce that the Tyne
OL,19,Fand Wear Metro will be extended to
OL,20,FWashington in the 2030s.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
