CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FThey also backed a major carbon
OL,7,Fcapture and storage facility on
OL,8,FTeesside though there have been
OL,9,Freports recently that the government
OL,10,Fare looking to find savings from those
OL,11,Fschemes to spend on defence.
OL,13,FMore than a dozen places in the North
OL,14,FEast are getting #20m in 'Pride in
OL,15,FPlace' funding for local regeneration
OL,16,Fprojects.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
