CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FAnd the region should see more
OL,7,Finvestment in the future following
OL,8,Fchanges to the Treasury 'Green Book',
OL,9,Fmeaning places down south where you're
OL,10,Foften calculated to get a bigger bang
OL,11,Ffor your buck are no longer
OL,12,Fprioritised.
OL,14,FNational policies with a particularly
OL,15,Fsignificant impact in our region
OL,16,Finclude increases to miners' pension
OL,17,Fpayments and scrapping the two-child
OL,18,Fbenefit cap - taking 67,000 local
OL,19,Fchildren out of poverty according to
OL,20,Fgovernment figures.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
