PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FThere's been a strong North East
OL,7,Fcabinet presence, with local MPs
OL,8,FBridget Phillipson, Anna Turley and
OL,9,FSir Alan Campbell joined by former
OL,10,Flocal MP Baroness Jenny Chapman.
OL,12,FAll of them may well be on their way
OL,13,Fout shortly after Starmer, as his
OL,14,Fsuccessor shapes their top team.
OL,16,FEverything points to Andy Burnham
OL,17,Fbeing that successor.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
