PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe won a high-stakes by-election last
OL,7,Fweek - with his ultimate ambitions
OL,8,Fabundantly clear, Labour MPs queuing
OL,9,Fup to support him and potential rivals
OL,10,Fstanding aside.
OL,12,FHe's long been nicknamed 'The King of
OL,13,Fthe North' - reflecting his profile as
OL,14,FMayor of Greater Manchester,
OL,15,Fparticularly after his battles with
OL,16,Fthe Conservative government over
OL,17,Ffinancial support during the pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe's spoken a lot about a north-south
OL,7,Fdivide and the need to decentralise
OL,8,Fand rebalance the country, by
OL,9,Finvesting more outside London and the
OL,10,FSouth East.
OL,12,FHe's likely to increase spending on
OL,13,Finfrastructure and give more powers to
OL,14,Fregional mayors.
OL,16,FOther policies could include major
OL,17,Fchanges to council tax, to the benefit
OL,18,Fof regions like the North East where
OL,19,Fproperty prices are cheaper.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
