PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FIt's been reported that he wants to
OL,7,Fmove part of the Downing Street
OL,8,Foperation to Manchester, similar to
OL,9,Fthe the government base the
OL,10,FConservatives set up in Darlington.
OL,12,FSo, Burnham clearly appears focused on
OL,13,Fimproving the prospects of the North
OL,14,Fof England - though our region may
OL,15,Fremind him that the North extends far
OL,16,Fbeyond Manchester.
OL,18,FTo date, we have all been reading a
OL,19,Flot into his past positions.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
