PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782749904
OL,3,CWhat does the change of Prime Minister
OL,4,Cmean for the North East?
OL,6,FHe is due to give a series of speeches
OL,7,Fover the next couple of weeks, setting
OL,8,Fout his plans and priorities now.
OL,10,FWith the Labour leadership election
OL,11,Flooking like a formality, Andy Burnham
OL,12,Fis due to become Prime Minister on 17
OL,13,FJuly.
OL,15,FThen we will start to find out what he
OL,16,Fcan deliver for the North East.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/11
